    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int CRYPT_MODE_CBC
      The cipher mode is cipher block chaining.
      static int CRYPT_MODE_CFB
      The cipher mode is cipher feedback (CFB).
      static int CRYPT_MODE_CTS
      The cipher mode is ciphertext stealing mode.
      static int CRYPT_MODE_ECB
      The cipher mode is electronic codebook.
      static int CRYPT_MODE_OFB
      The cipher mode is Output Feedback (OFB).
